cff-version: 1.2.0
title: OceanDataTools
message: If you use this toolbox, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: software

authors:
  - family-names: Gonzalez Rodriguez
    given-names: Eduardo
    affiliation: CICESE
    email: egonzale@cicese.mx

abstract: >
  OceanDataTools is a MATLAB toolbox for processing, analyzing,
  and visualizing oceanographic datasets. The toolbox includes
  tools for eddy detection and tracking, front detection,
  stratification diagnostics, climatology generation,
  geographic utilities, and visualization tools.

keywords:
  - oceanography
  - MATLAB
  - eddies
  - ocean fronts
  - geostrophic velocity
  - climatology
  - remote sensing

license: MIT

repository-code: https://github.com/USER/OceanDataTools
url: https://github.com/USER/OceanDataTools

version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-01-01

